 Pure Noise 发行他们的第三张唱片，其中包括与<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/artists/motionless-in-white">Motionless In White</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/poppy">Poppy</a>和 Chris Motionless 的合作。</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，这张专辑的标题来自主唱布莱恩·加里斯 (Bryan Garris) 在飞机上与坐在他旁边的一位女士的一次谈话。当他承认他发现控制飞行的“边缘恐惧症”特别困难时，她告诉他，“在你应该去的地方你不会去。”</p><p> “在这张专辑中，我们走得最快；我们经历了有史以来最可怕的一次。我们还推出了有史以来最朗朗上口、旋律最优美的歌曲，这就是重点，”吉他手艾萨克·黑尔 (Isaac Hale) 说道。 “我们不想局限于某个特定方向，而是希望涵盖所有方向。” </p><figure id="attachment_3593751" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3593751" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3593751" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-.jpg" alt="Knocked Loose 专辑《You Won&#39;t Go Before You&#39;s Shoulds To》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS--150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS--400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS--800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS--696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS--1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Knocked-Loose-You-Wont-Go-Before-Youre-Supposed-To-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS--1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3593751" clas